{
  "text": "And therefore also that E k \u2113 \u2212 E g \u2113 > \u03b4 g \u2113+1 \u2212 \u03b4 k \u2113+1 [CITATION_1] By rearranging the definition of \u03b4 k i with i = \u2113 + 1 we get that",
